						               													<description>RoleChess &amp;#10;is a combination of Chess and a role game that is played with pieces similar to those used in Chess. The movements of pieces differ a bit from those of the pieces used in Chess. Nevertheless, the biggest difference from Chess is in the progress of the game. &amp;#10;Different types of pieces possess an energy amount of their own, and additionally, they have certain attack and defense coefficients, which when multiplied by the number of spots of a dice, determine the attack or defense score of the piece in question in a battle. The difference between the attack and defense score affects the energy amount to be lost by the pieces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The aim of the game is to reduce the opponent&amp;rsquo;s Emperor&amp;rsquo;s energy amount to zero, while at the same time protecting one&amp;rsquo;s own Emperor from the same fate. The player who is the first to beat the opponent&amp;rsquo;s Emperor will win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Product materials&amp;#10;Board and pieces are fully made of real wood. Game board is made of pine tree and game pieces are made of basswood. Game box is made of cardboard.&amp;#10;Product is designed in Finland and is manufactured in China. All components used in this product are environmentally friendly and information is found of all components. Product has a CE marking.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
